00:05:34.199 --> 00:05:39.480
The type of God he is, he does good to people.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:44.519
The friends here tell us very often that they really feel the help and comfort from the

00:05:44.519 --> 00:05:46.800
brothers that are far.

