00:06:05.839 --> 00:06:13.000
I felt a calm, a peaceful calm feeling that Jehovah is going to take care of.

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:14.000
Why are you worrying about?

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:18.720
Jehovah is going to take care of us and don't put your choice and mind on nothing,

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.560
